# ThreadSanitizer suppressions for anolis-provider-bread.
#
# Format: https://github.com/google/sanitizers/wiki/ThreadSanitizerSuppressions
# Scope third-party / known-benign races ONLY. Never suppress first-party
# (anolis_provider_bread::) races — fix those. The TSAN lane runs with these
# applied; the first run per change is a triage pass (read the tsan-report
# artifact, then add a precise entry here for each confirmed false positive).

# --- abseil (pulled in transitively by protobuf) -------------------------
# abseil's internal synchronization primitives use intentional/benign races
# on their own fast paths; these are well-documented upstream false positives.
race:absl::base_internal::SpinLock
race:absl::synchronization_internal::
race:absl::base_internal::LowLevelAlloc

# --- protobuf ------------------------------------------------------------
# Lazy global/once initialization inside libprotobuf.
race:google::protobuf::internal::
